data.description: Beautiful 1 Story home available on an oversized lot. This home features 3 great size bedrooms plus a office/study and 2.5 bathrooms, Fully Fenced Back Yard, Open kitchen area to the living room with gas fireplace and high ceilings, Tile Flooring in main living areas. The backyard is landscaped and has a great sized covered patio. Primary bathroom includes separate shower and soaking tub with dual sinks with quartz. The utility room and additional half bath rate located near the garage. This home is walking distance to community pool/ parks/ and tennis courts. Low taxes in this area. Call for an appointment!
